  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this multicenter randomized phase II trial is to determine the efficacy of
      sorafenib and irinotecan combination versus irinotecan monotherapy or versus sorafenib
      monotherapy in metastatic colorectal cancer patients with KRAS mutated tumors after failure
      of all active drugs known to be effective.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
